{
  "texts": [
    "We do run our validation set with ChatGPT4 and Gemini Pro.",
    "Pre-trained Transformer (GPT) model.",
    "4 ChatGPT is fine-tuned to closely follow instructions using a process called reinforcement learning from human feedback (RLHF).",
    "This method enhances the GPT model by having humans review its responses.",
    "Based on their evaluations, the model's parameters are adjusted to generate more desirable responses (Ouyang et al., 2022)."
  ]
}